{"tid":2073050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[等成個鐘都唔撚笑]侵侵為新冠取名「功夫」（kung flu）","createTime":"2020-06-21T04:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T05:08:26.000Z","uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef97b1632a27c607216823b0c9a4a3410838ac7","tid":2073050,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEqeAse.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEqeAse.gif&h=35d29e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6813/4650027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6813%2F4650027&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2YwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=cd8e1cb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6813/4650027</a><br />\n<br />\n川普為新冠取名「功夫」（kung flu）！再涉種族歧視<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/21/BSdJ3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F21%2FBSdJ3u.jpg&h=f99bee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統川普20日在土耳沙的造勢大會上用種族歧視字眼形容新冠肺炎，他為它取名「功夫（感冒）」（kung flu），與中國功夫（kung fu）諧音，逗得現場的支持者哈哈大笑。<br />\n<br />\n川普說：「這是疾病，毫無疑問，它的名字比史上任何疾病都多。我可以取名「功夫（感冒）」，我可以取19個不同的名字。許多人稱它為病毒，許多人稱它為感冒，有什麼差別？我想我們有19或20種不同的名稱。」<br />\n<br />\n這是川普首次使用「kung flu」稱呼新冠肺炎，他之前稱新冠病毒是「中國病毒」，被批評種族歧視，並掀起美國社會的反華人歧視。"},{"pid":"5dcf2590b202edb2b23317be55c3d9329d712ba8","tid":2073050,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVvmZUj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVvmZUj.jpg&h=6993f567&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"088dad8ca6b59f4811b8ad794760f105af6ad5e1","tid":2073050,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"民主黨支持者幾乎都係華人多"},{"pid":"d1017ed76679afd8bb6eb9a7e5187784c6ed43f9","tid":2073050,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"共flu"},{"pid":"0a2303d07322683b182292210e83ab3015d1e841","tid":2073050,"uid":274435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"叫東亞病flu"},{"pid":"9434944f9589fcbec5e2000ca0d5129cc8d6de90","tid":2073050,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a2303d07322683b182292210e83ab3015d1e841","tid":2073050,"uid":274435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"叫東亞病flu"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2831a9b5498cbcbd03f26b58d8e61289c3e8a1ba","tid":2073050,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"088dad8ca6b59f4811b8ad794760f105af6ad5e1","tid":2073050,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"民主黨支持者幾乎都係華人多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"Solomon? Yan can cook 個主持"},{"pid":"71ef155d3a20b3bfc5295735e7975fd808995d97","tid":2073050,"uid":354682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2116be231c0cf99b5560d1f06fc51938d3288e","tid":2073050,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"CCP Flu針對中共<br />\n但Kung Flu真係歧視華人<br />\n尤其係Kung Fu本身係廣東話譯成"},{"pid":"326258652f14ed891fcb4e2c45e7c9f09918c690","tid":2073050,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy